data.description: Welcome to your Naples sanctuary! This exquisite property features 3 beds plus a den and 2 baths, seamlessly blending elegance and comfort to offer an unparalleled Florida lifestyle. As you step inside, your gaze will be  captivated by the serene preserve view, providing a tranquil backdrop to your living space. Each room boasts volume ceilings and tasteful plantation shutters, elevating the overall ambiance. The chef's kitchen is a culinary haven, equipped with stainless steel appliances and adorned with granite countertops. Step outside to discover a true outdoor paradise, complete with a private pool and spa that beckons you to relax and immerse yourself in the peaceful surroundings. The generously-sized screened lanai extends your outdoor living space, offering a covered seating area that's perfect for alfresco dining. As an added bonus, residents of Reflection Lakes have access to a variety of amenities. Plus, you'll be delighted to know that HOA fees are attractively low, and there are no CDD fees to contend with. Located just minutes from Route 41, seize this opportunity to make this Naples gem your own. Start living the Southwest Florida lifestyle you've always envisioned!
